Package org.ejbca.core.model.approval.profile

Class ApprovalStep

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ejbca.core.model.approval.profile.ApprovalStep
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class ApprovalStep
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class represents an approval step, to sum of which is a collective series of events, in serial order, which must occur for an approval to pass. Once the final step passes, the approval automatically passes. Steps are stored in the ApprovalProfile without order, but instead track their own order in the form of a doubly linked list.
